\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢team人去咗邊度，DLLM</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb2b9de69d739eb710e492efa0da313678c23e74","tid":1868594,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"世界上唔會有慈善機構<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"807e9a27267780c95f8ef142aa3f5a25c0a5bb4a","tid":1868594,"uid":221270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無國界醫生是一個獨立的國際醫療人道救援組織<br />\n致力為受武裝衝突、流行病、疫病和天災影響，以及遭排拒於醫療體系以外的人群提供緊急醫療援助。無國界醫生只會基於人們的需要提供援助，不受種族、宗教、性別或政治因素左右。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淨係識話會向公眾推行健康教育，對香港武漢肺炎疫情冇做到咩應對工作，咩醫療援助都冇，香港人個個月捐錢俾你為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"234e4b0cb7a597cb3afc5d875df4af69ff5bd66a","tid":1868594,"uid":152577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f83a0db82c025f22ce024d9c17b9ab36745c927","tid":1868594,"uid":183473,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"個班係今次WARS冇幫香港人做過嘢嘅慈善機構，我發誓以後一分一毫都唔會再捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c815df339c431e668242defe8039492827a9b37","tid":1868594,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"可能祈緊禱"},{"pid":"298801489eb75a91e953c51b37e84ecec9341b78","tid":1868594,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141c16d5e83cb6909abb2ca2881cbcf77e99dfcf","tid":1868594,"uid":221270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成班垃圾慈善機構"},{"pid":"da5a3c70c7b1183b7